lly related to the accident? Is there pre-existing damage unrelated to the accident? The book additionally offers numerous case examples, including assessments and expert opinions, as well as help with report preparation based on sample expert reports.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 4aBildgebende Diagnostik. 4aDamage imaging. 4aGutachten. 4aPosttraumatische Schäden. 4aSchadensbeurteilung. 4aSchadensbilder. 4adamage assessment. 4adiagnostic imaging. 4aexpert reports. 4apost-traumatic damage. 70(DE-601)1042213130(DE-588)4074675-6aMedizinisches Gutachten2gnd 70(DE-601)1044098000(DE-588)4006617-4aBildgebendes Verfahren2gnd 70(DE-601)1044594090(DE-588)4006318-5aBewegungsapparat2gnd 70(DE-601)1044938950(DE-588)4032844-2aKrankheit2gnd 70(DE-601)1057481100(DE-588)4124397-3aVerletzung2gnd 7aMEDICAL / Radiology, Radiotherapy & Nuclear Medicine.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2017z9783110548211oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831105179890 cprintz978311051793440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110519525423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110519525.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA1ALL  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPMb2017